'''platform''' - Template for platform-specific technical information on games.darkrepos.com

==Description==

Displays technical ROM information in a compact format for different gaming platforms. This replaces the old platform-specific templates like {{NES}}, {{SNES}}, etc.

==Usage==

<pre>
{{platform
| platform = NES
| mapper = MMC5
| prg_rom = 512 KB
| chr_rom = 256 KB
| prg_ram = 8 KB
| mirroring = Vertical
| battery = yes
}}
</pre>

==Parameters==

===Common Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| platform || Yes || Platform name (NES, SNES, GBA, GB, GBC, Genesis, etc.)
|}

===NES-Specific Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
| mapper || iNES mapper number or name (MMC1, MMC3, MMC5, etc.)
|-
| prg_rom || PRG ROM size
|-
| chr_rom || CHR ROM size
|-
| prg_ram || PRG RAM size
|-
| chr_ram || CHR RAM size
|-
| mirroring || Screen mirroring (Horizontal, Vertical, 4-screen)
|-
| battery || Battery-backed save (yes/no)
|}

===SNES-Specific Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
| mapper || ROM type (LoROM, HiROM, ExHiROM, SA-1, etc.)
|-
| rom_size || Total ROM size
|-
| sram || SRAM size
|-
| expansion || Expansion chips (DSP-1, SA-1, SuperFX, etc.)
|}

===GBA-Specific Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
| rom_size || ROM size
|-
| save_type || Save type (SRAM, EEPROM, Flash)
|-
| save_size || Save size
|}

==Example: NES Game==

{{platform
| platform = NES
| mapper = MMC5
| prg_rom = 512 KB
| chr_rom = 256 KB
| prg_ram = 8 KB
| mirroring = Vertical
| battery = yes
}}

==Example: SNES Game==

{{platform
| platform = SNES
| mapper = LoROM
| rom_size = 2 MB
| sram = 64 KB
}}

